Sure, here are some examples:

1. Kuce *mi* je obojila u plavo. (My *dog* painted my house in blue.) 
2. Kada sam stigao kući, *kuca* me je dočekala na vratima. (When I arrived home, my *dog* greeted me at the door.)
3. *Kuća* mi je mala, ali je jako udobna. (My *house* is small, but very cozy.)
4. Moj prijatelj radi kao *kuvar* u jednoj kafani. (My friend works as a *cook* in a restaurant.)
5. Sinoć smo se svi okupili kod *kuće* i igrali društvene igre. (Last night we all gathered at my *house* and played board games.)
6. Kada je pala kiša, *kucica* na drvetu je postala sklonište za ptice. (When it rained, the *little house* on the tree became a shelter for birds.)
7. *Kucni* ljubimci su mi jako važni i volim da ih mazim. (My *domestic* pets are very important to me and I love to cuddle them.)
8. Nakon dugog putovanja, napokon smo stigli u *gostinjsku kuću* gde ćemo provesti sledećih nekoliko dana. (After a long journey, we finally arrived at our *guest house* where we will spend the next few days.)

Note: In the sentences above, the word "kuce" was highlighted with an asterisk (*).